<a href="http://www.theeastafrican.co.ke/news/Comesa-Sadc-imports-get-tariff-relief-again-/-/2558/1658344/-/ugt2mi/-/index.html" target="_self">http://www.theeastafrican.co.ke/news/Comesa-Sadc-imports-get-tariff-reli...</a></p><p><i>The Star</i>, ‘Border trade stalls as Uganda suspends agents’, 5 January 2013</p><p>
